title: SoftBank shares surge 10% after telecom unit lifts outlook, Arm strength bolsters AI narrative
summary_full: Shares of SoftBank Group Corp jumped over 10% after its telecom arm raised its full-year profit outlook and renewed optimism around Arm Holdings.
summary_public: Shares of SoftBank Group Corp jumped over 10% after its telecom arm raised its full-year profit outlook and renewed optimism around Arm Holdings.
